(204, 1, '2018-05-11 18:37:55', '2018-05-11 18:37:55', '<div class=\"pdp-product-desc \">\r\n<div class=\"html-content pdp-product-highlights\">\r\n<ul class=\"\">\r\n 	<li class=\"\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2o4n.pdp.product_detail.i5.255d2469Y0wvXA\">Điện Xoay 360 độ Tương Tác Mèo Lông Đồ Chơi, áo gile \\ t \\ t \\ t \\ t \\ t \\ t \\ táo gile funny and thú vị, tuyệt vời chơi đồ chơi chợ sweetie.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\">Có thể tháo rời, you can giữ it mình to chơi đùa cùng thú cưng of you.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\">Đồ chơi đĩa chứa một màu xanh bóng, nên bạn cũng có thể đặt một số catnip hay ăn vặt vào đồ chơi đĩa, có thể thu hút nhỏ of mèo con chú ý.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\">Sự phát triển thể chất and trí não, cảm xúc and hành vi có thể tất cả các ảnh hưởng this vui chơi lành mạnh.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"\">MỘT thực sự món quà tốt cho bạn bè of you bất cứ ai có vật nuôi or riêng of bạn thú cưng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"html-content detail-content\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2o4n.pdp.product_detail.i4.255d2469Y0wvXA\">Electric 360 Degree Rotate Interactive Cat Feather Toys, funny and interesting, amazing playing toys for your sweetie.\r\nRemovable, you can hold it yourself to play with your pet.\r\nThe toy plate contains a blue ball, so you can also put some catnip or snacks into the toy plate, which can attract the little kitten\'s attention.\r\nPhysical and mental development, emotions and behavior can all be influenced by this healthy play.\r\nA really good gift for your friends anyone who has pets or your own pets.\r\nFeatures：\r\n1. Three ways to use: You can use cat toys as a plate cat toy with inside bell ball, a hand-held cat teaser with feathers, and also a spin electric cat toy!\r\n2. Two AAA batteries required (Not Included).\r\n3. Irregular spinning: Our cat toys move in an irregular time with clockwise and counter-clockwise circles with a bell ball inside.\r\n4. Stable base: The plate base with anti-skid pad, which makes it stable and difficult to turn over by cats.\r\nInstructions for use:\r\n1. First open the battery container, Put two AAA batteries into the battery container.\r\n2. Please put the product on a flat surface, then press the on /off button to start.\r\n3. Top feathers are designed to rotate in a random, moving in an irregular with clockwise and counter-clockwise circles.\r\n4. With a ball on the plate. The cat can play with the ball.\r\n5. About the toy\'s chassis section, you can completely disassemble and clean it.\r\nSpecifications:\r\nMaterial: ABS\r\nBase diameter: approx 20cm/ 7.87inch\r\nPillars length: 15cm/ 5.9inch\r\nRod length: approx 17cm/ 6.69inch\r\nToys length: approx 20cm/ 7.87inch\r\nPower: 2 AAA batteries(Not Included)\r\nPackage:\r\n1 x Funny Cat Toy\r\nNote:\r\nFor pets only.\r\nContains small parts,keep out of reach of children.\r\nPets should be supervised while playing with this toy.\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://vn-live.slatic.net/v2/resize/products/S-100040972-2528501f2c3858140858ddc0dbd75cf7.jpg\" width=\"600\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2o4n.pdp.product_detail.i3.255d2469Y0wvXA\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://vn-live.slatic.net/v2/resize/products/S-100040972-93bc9d4070930627de36e9009e8a251f.jpg\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://vn-live.slatic.net/v2/resize/products/S-100040972-05fdeb438b4d2747797df5f8ea3e9e68.jpg\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-mod-specification\">\r\n<h2 class=\"pdp-mod-section-title \">Đặc tính sản phẩm</h2>\r\n<div class=\"pdp-general-features\">\r\n<ul class=\"specification-keys\">\r\n 	<li class=\"key-li\"><span class=\"key-title\">Thương hiệu</span>\r\n<div class=\"html-content key-value\">OEM</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"key-li\"><span class=\"key-title\">SKU</span>\r\n<div class=\"html-content key-value\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2o4n.pdp.product_detail.i1.255d2469Y0wvXA\">OE680OTAAADM90VNAMZ-20855916</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"key-li\"><span class=\"key-title